<gpx xmlns="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1" xmlns:gpxx="http://www.garmin.com/xmlschemas/GpxExtensions/v3" creator="CALTOPO" version="1.1"><metadata><name><![CDATA[La Tierra]]></name></metadata><trk><name>La Tierra</name><desc>Popularity: 4/5
Difficulty: 1/5
Dates: 10/1 - 6/1
Parking: La Cuchara Trailhead is a dirt lot with plenty of parking, there are several other nearby trailheads if La Cuchara is full.

La Tierra is one of Santa Fe's city trail systems. It's very close to town and has 25 miles of heavily interwoven trailhead. You can design a hundreds of different routes in La Tierra, and this is just one to get you started. There are a lot of intersections, but they are extremely well signed, with maps and intersection numbers.

La Tierra is fairly flat with few steep climbs and lots of easy rolling terrain which makes for great runs where you can enter flow state. This route is one of my favorites when I'm doing a shorter run at La Tierra, but once you get familiar with the trail system you can go crazy creating your own routes. Get out and explore! </desc><trkseg><trkpt lat="35.70936554673201" lon="-105.9667408904507"><ele>2158.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.709361250291366" lon="-105.96674333411022"><ele>2158.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70936" lon="-105.96674000000002"><ele>2158.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70936563553682" lon="-105.96675502809819"><ele>2158.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70939" lon="-105.96681999999998"><ele>2158.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70938" lon="-105.96692000000002"><ele>2157.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70932" lon="-105.96699000000001"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70932" lon="-105.96712000000002"><ele>2155.7746168873273</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70937" lon="-105.96719999999999"><ele>2155.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70947" lon="-105.96744999999999"><ele>2155.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70947" lon="-105.96744999999999"><ele>2155.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70947" lon="-105.96744999999999"><ele>2155.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70939" lon="-105.96769"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70939" lon="-105.96769"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70927" lon="-105.96771999999999"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70912" lon="-105.96780000000001"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70901" lon="-105.96780000000001"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70881" lon="-105.96769999999998"><ele>2155.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70859" lon="-105.96780000000001"><ele>2155.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70828" lon="-105.96812999999997"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70818" lon="-105.96830999999997"><ele>2155.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70805" lon="-105.96859999999998"><ele>2156.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.70805" lon="-10